Package: crumblr
Type: Package
Title: Count ratio uncertainty modeling base linear regression
Version: 0.99.4
Date: 2022-11-08
Authors@R: person("Gabriel", "Hoffman", role=c("aut", "cre"), email="gabriel.hoffman@mssm.edu")
Description: Crumblr enables analysis of count ratio data using weighted linear (mixed) models.  This is useful for fast approximation to GLMs and GLMM's.  A variance stabilizing transform (vst) based on this model enables improved clustering and PCA.
VignetteBuilder: knitr
License: Artistic-2.0
Encoding: UTF-8
URL: https://gabrielhoffman.github.io/crumblr
